data.title: Overflow Worship Leaders Online
data.meta_description: Overflow Worship Leaders Online equips worship leaders in volunteer supported churches through online self paced video courses, on demand video resources and livestream trainings.
data.text:
Are you tired of racing from Sunday to Sunday at an unsustainable pace?

Are you searching for training and tools that are relevant to your ministry and leadership goals?

Overflow Worship Leaders Online is designed to help you increase your capacity, lead from wholeness, and step fully into your unique calling in worship ministry.

Andrea Olson is Founder of Overflow Worship and Overflow Worship Leaders Online. She herself is a passionate worship leader, songwriter, and worship-leading coach in Minnesota. She founded these organizations out of her dedication to to encouraging worship leaders to thrive with what they have, wherever they are in their journey.

Andrea has coached worship leaders from all over the country and written with award winning songwriters such as Paul Baloche, Meredith Andrews, Dustin Smith and more. She is an Amazon best selling author and worship leader who is passionate about educating and equipping current and upcoming worship leaders to thrive for the long haul.

As worship leaders, the business of ministry is life-giving and exciting. But sometimes it can also leave us feeling alone and drained. Overflow Worship Leaders Online is committed to providing uplifting community and expert support for every step of your journey.

We have packed thousands of dollars worth of content into this site, but we know you've got a ministry budget! So, our prices are tailored with you in mind. We've made it affordable, even if you have to pay out of your own pocket because your church has a limited budget.

You can get unlimited access to all of this for only $199.99 per year (this option includes bonuses and discounts available only to our annual members adding up to more than the cost of the membership itself! Keep scrolling to learn what they are!)

Alternatively, if you have a very limited budget, you can pay just $19.99 per month if you prefer to pay as you go!

Andrea Olson is Founder of Overflow Worship and Overflow Worship Leaders Online. She herself is a passionate worship leader, songwriter, and worship-leading coach in Minnesota. She founded these organizations out of her dedication to to encouraging worship leaders to thrive with what they have, wherever they are in their journey.

Meredith Andrews is a passionate worship leader and Dove Award-winning artist. Songwriter of “Open Up The Heavens”, “Not For A Moment,” “Lamb of God,” and more! Meredith is passionate about worship and writing songs that bring healing and hope through leading people into the presence of God. Meredith is a guest speaker inside the membership, and a frequent live guest at our annual in person conference!

David Lanning has years of training experience, from vocalists to bands. David is the former program director of CTI Music Ministries and is now the Worship Director at Refuge Church in Willmar, MN. David brings a unique perspective from his years of training full time evangelistic music teams both in music skill and spiritually. He is a favorite guest speaker at Overflow Worship Leaders Online.

Owner of NLFX Professional, an award-winning industry leader for your audio, video, lighting, integration services, and more, Ben brings decades of experience to our members in the area of sound and lighting. He is a frequent guest inside the membership through a series of live episodes co-hosted with Andrea Olson addressing the top pain points for worship leaders in the area of sound and lighting.

A three-time Dove Award-winning songwriter, Paul travels the globe teaching and leading others in worship. Through Leadworship.com, he developed a series of Master Classes designed to equip and train leaders and worship teams worldwide. He also served as a Worship Pastor in Texas for over 25 years. Paul is a vault of wisdom that he generously shares with our members. His sessions leave you with pages of notes for immediate practical application.

Overflow Worship has encouraged and helped our leaders and team. It is very helpful, professional, God-focused, and beneficial. Don’t hesitate to join; you will find applicable information to help you and your team grow stronger musically and spiritually.

- Luke from grace life church
